00:27:30,410 --> 00:27:32,911
Or Jim Avery...
he's our alderman.

416
00:27:32,913 --> 00:27:34,579
Deputy Grimly...

417
00:27:34,581 --> 00:27:37,616
Oh, that's the fella,
Deputy Grimly.

