00:28:18,724 --> 00:28:20,057
No, sir.

436
00:28:20,059 --> 00:28:22,159
I'm a cautious driver
by nature,

437
00:28:22,161 --> 00:28:23,993
on account of my eyesight.

438
00:28:23,995 --> 00:28:26,095
Glaucoma, they say it is.

439
00:28:26,097 --> 00:28:28,998
Only in the one eye,
but you can't be too careful.

440
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,967
<i>That's what I tell
my parishioners.</i>

441
00:28:30,969 --> 00:28:33,336
- Deputy Grimly...
- <i>Forgiveness...</i>

442
00:28:33,338 --> 00:28:34,904
that's the heart
of the Good Book.

443
00:28:34,906 --> 00:28:37,240
Turn the other cheek,
second chances, Amen.

444
00:28:37,242 --> 00:28:40,176
So, no, I don't hold a grudge
