if he had any pets.

462
00:29:43,379 --> 00:29:44,779
Oh, yeah?

463
00:29:44,781 --> 00:29:46,781
Was it, uh, this fella maybe?

464
00:29:46,783 --> 00:29:48,149
<i>Yeah.</i>

