for the suspect...</i>

497
00:31:11,998 --> 00:31:13,231
Lorne Malvo.

498
00:31:13,233 --> 00:31:15,066
He used it
to check into a motel.

499
00:31:15,068 --> 00:31:17,569
Lorne Malvo, huh?

500
00:31:17,571 --> 00:31:20,270
Oh, they're... they're coming out.
I'll call you back.

501
00:31:20,272 --> 00:31:21,905
<i>Sorry again for
the confusion, Pastor.</i>

502
00:31:21,907 --> 00:31:24,174
Oh, just glad nobody got hurt.

503
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:30,514
You're letting him go?

504
00:31:30,516 --> 00:31:31,715
Desk duty, two weeks.

505
00:31:31,717 --> 00:31:33,784
- Now, just a...
- Three weeks.

506
00:31:33,786 --> 00:31:35,252
For Pete...

507
00:31:35,254 --> 00:31:36,987
You're making a mistake.

508
00:31:45,630 --> 00:31:48,864
<i>Grimly, with me, now.</i>

509
00:31:51,134 --> 00:31:53,469
You pointed your service weapon
at a civilian...

510
00:31:53,471 --> 00:31:55,638
no, a damn minister
on a public street.

511
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,573
No evidence, no fingerprints,
nothing.

512
00:31:57,575 --> 00:31:59,575
What about the picture?

513
00:31:59,577 --> 00:32:00,810
Oh, that Zapruder film
in the file?

514
00:32:00,812 --> 00:32:02,245
Hell, son,
that could be a photo

515
00:32:02,247 --> 00:32:03,579
of my mama, for all I know.

516
00:32:03,581 --> 00:32:05,248
No, it's him.
I know it's him.

517
00:32:05,250 --> 00:32:07,083
Negatory.
We checked his story.

518
00:32:07,085 --> 00:32:09,318
- It tracks.
- He's lying!

519
00:32:27,169 --> 00:32:29,771
You have a blessed day.

